				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Can bards powerlevel?<a name="18724"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 3 04 11:06 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Charm PL works VERY quickly indeed.  ALL of their skills suffer, however.  Simply singing AE snare or slow, or single pulling with targetted snare, will hold aggro while they beat on it.  This is not super fast or anything.  But it DOES pretty much ensure that they never die, saving xp and CR time etc.  The advantage here, is that their offensive skills get some work at least.  Defense, of course, will still suck.
<br />

<br />
If what you want is levels, and want em fast?  CHARM PL.</span></td>
