				<td colspan="2"><span>the 2 ways ive PL friends or my alt wiz.
<br />

<br />
1.  get up your best Ae snare song, not one with a dot preferably.  get a handful of low level mobs (appropriate for your friend(s)) and let them pound away and get the xp.  thier melee skills will rise as can their casting skills, but they will get no defense skills as you keep 100% agro.  this works well until low 30s, then things can start to beat you down rather well.
<br />

<br />
2.  swarm kite and let them join your group.  did this last night with my 39th wiz in dulak.  i only made a few % xp on 2 swarms on Lady Di, but my wiz made over 20% xp.  that includes a death because charm broke early and i was playing and let my wiz nuke 1 time.  big mistake on my part.  could not get agro back off the mob that was not my pet so dead wiz.  no biggy.</span></td>
